  "summary": "Mattermost doesn't set permissions on downloaded bulk export",
  "details": "Mattermost versions 11.4.x <= 11.4.0, 11.3.x <= 11.3.1, 11.2.x <= 11.2.3, 10.11.x <= 10.11.11 fail to set permissions on downloaded bulk export which allows other local users on the server to be able to read contents of the bulk export. Mattermost Advisory ID: MMSA-2026-00593.",
